General.Name: Fsport AB
General.Description: FSport AB (publ), a gaming and media platform company, provides mobile sports games in Sweden. The company creates and delivers fair and genuinely entertaining sports betting on a proprietary platform. It operates FSport.se provides daily fantasy sports; 1X2.se, a gaming portal that delivers the gaming tips for sports and online gaming; and Trav.se, a gaming portal provides daily betting tips with place and winner bets from trotting races in and outside Sweden. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is based in Helsingborg, Sweden.
